Multidimensional Personality Inventory for Chinese Adolescent

nobody

2023-08-28

mdta <- read.csv("mdta.csv", h = T)
dim(mdta)
[1] 851  98
mdta <- mdta %>% 
  mutate_if(is.integer, as.numeric) %>%
  mutate_all(na_if, 9) %>%
  drop_na()

dim(mdta)
[1] 793  98

Force-directed Algorithms

mpi_zeroorder <- cor(mdta)
  • the positioning of odes in a force-directed algorithm cannot be interpreted.
qgraph(mpi_zeroorder, layout="spring",
          groups = list("En" = 1:20,
                        "Ha" = 21:37,
                        "Pe" = 38:51,
                        "De" = 52:65,
                        "Ca" = 66:77,
                        "To" = 78:89,
                        "Up" = 90:98),
          color = c("lightblue","lightsalmon",
                               "lightgreen", "lightpink",
                               "lightgrey", "cornsilk", "azure"))

Multidimensional Scaling MDS

  • convert the correlation matrix into a dissimilarity matrix
dissimilarity_mpi <- sim2diss(mpi_zeroorder)
  • convert the correlation matrix into a dissimilarity matrix
  • locate points (configuration matrix) in a two-dim space
mpi_MDS <- mds(dissimilarity_mpi)
head(round(mpi_MDS$conf, 2))
       D1    D2
En1 -0.23 -0.45
En2 -0.31 -0.20
En3 -0.40 -0.57
En4 -0.22 -0.58
En5 -0.25 -0.69
En6 -0.47 -0.31

Transforamtion

mpi_MDS_ordinal <- mds(dissimilarity_mpi, type="ordinal")
plot(mpi_MDS_ordinal, plot.type = "Shepard", main="Ordinal")
text(1.1,0.3, paste("Stress =", round(mpi_MDS_ordinal$stress,2)))

mpi_MDS_ratio <- mds(dissimilarity_mpi, type="ratio")
plot(mpi_MDS_ratio, plot.type = "Shepard", main="Ratio")
text(1.1,0.3, paste("Stress =", round(mpi_MDS_ratio$stress,2)))

mpi_MDS_interval <- mds(dissimilarity_mpi, type="interval")
plot(mpi_MDS_interval, plot.type = "Shepard", main="Interval")
text(1.1,0.3, paste("Stress =", round(mpi_MDS_interval$stress,2)))

mpi_MDS_mspline <- mds(dissimilarity_mpi, type="mspline")
plot(mpi_MDS_mspline, plot.type = "Shepard", main="Spline")
text(1.1,0.3, paste("Stress =", round(mpi_MDS_mspline$stress,2)))
